      <title>汇丰新任首席执行官在全体员工会议上要求员工关注成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/hsbc-s-new-ceo-tells-staff-to-keep-an-eye-on-costs-in-town-hall</link>
